2004-08-17 10:02 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron at xharbour.com>
  * source/rtl/regex.c
    + Added support of precompiled regex to HB_AtX()
    ! Corrected HB_AtX() to return starting position which considers the the start offset
      (to be compatiable with At() extended functionality)

    /* Note if anyone wqs using HB_AtX() with start offset such code will need to be corrected. */

  * source/vm/memvars.c
