2004-08-16 14:44 UTC+0200 Maurilio Longo <maurilio.longo@libero.it>
  * source/rtl/gtapi.c
    ! fixed hb_gtGetCursor(), read comment there, this one fixes this
      sample code:

      procedure main()

      setcursor(3)
      devpos(row(),MaxCol()-11)
      devout(Replicate("a", 10))
      ? setcursor()
      inkey(0)

      devpos(row()+1,MaxCol()-10)
      devout(Replicate("b",11))
      ? setcursor()
      inkey(0)
     return

2004-08-14 12:00 UTC-0300 Eduardo Fernandes <modalsist@yahoo.com.br>
