2004-08-12 21:40 UTC+0530 Pritpal Bedi <pritpal@vouchcac.com>
  * xharbour/source/rtl/memoline.c
    Changed if( ulPos < ulLen || (ulLineNumber == ulLines && ulLineEnd >= ulLineBegin) )
    to      if( ulPos <= ulLen || ( ulLineNumber == ulLines && ulLineEnd >= ulLineBegin ) )

    Clipper returns empty line if last line of memo is terminated by CRLF pair
    xHarbour was returning NULL.

