2004-07-26 03:36 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron at xharbour.com>
  * source/rtl/objfunc.prg
    * Some correction of iconsistencies.

  * include/classes.h
  * source/vm/classes.c
  * source/vm/hvm.c
    + Added support for using native types as objects.

  * source/rtl/tclass.prg
    + Added basic classes definitions for native types.

  * include/hbclass.ch
    + Added support for new syntax:
      ENABLE TYPE CLASS ARRAY|BLOCK|CHARACTER|DATE|LOGICAL|NUMERIC|POINTER

      EXTEND [TYPE] ARRAY|BLOCK|CHARACTER|DATE|LOGICAL|NUMERIC|POINTER WITH METHOD <SomeFunc>
      EXTEND [TYPE] ARRAY|BLOCK|CHARACTER|DATE|LOGICAL|NUMERIC|POINTER WITH MESSAGE <SomeMessage> METHOD <SomeFunc>

      OVERRIDE METHOD <SomeMethod> [IN] CLASS <SomeClass> WITH [METHOD] <SomeFunc> [SCOPE <Scope>]
      EXTEND CLASS <SomeClass> WITH METHOD <SomeFunc>
      EXTEND CLASS <SomeClass> WITH METHOD <SomeFunc>
      EXTEND CLASS <SomeClass> WITH MESSAGE <SomeMessage> METHOD <SomeFunc>

  + tests/enbltype.prg
    + New sample to demonstrate enabling and utilization of native types as extendable objects.

  + tests/exttype.prg
     + New sample to demonstrate extension of native types with OUT using any class deinitions.

  + tests/extend.prg
     + New sample to demonstrate how to extend normal classes as well as native type base classes.

  + tests/override.prg
    + New sample to demonstrate how to override methods of existing classes as well as native type base classes.

