2004-07-24 17:58 UTC-0500 Vicente Guerra <vicente@guerra.com.mx>
  * source/rtl/tbrowse.prg
    ! Fixed bug which leaves "blank" lines at the top of the browse.
    - Removed ::ForceStabilize(). ::ForceStable() performs all the work.
    - Removed ::lInitRow. It was used only in ::ForceStabilize(), but
      wasn't used in ::stabilize().
    - Removed ::DrawRows(). It was integrated to ::DrawARow(), so there
      will not be double code for the same task.

